{"tid":1261174,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"京東方展示全新LCD顯示屏：對比度達百萬級，功耗比OLED低40%","createTime":"2019-06-27T06:09:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T02:03:33.000Z","uid":141060,"like":3,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4f977f94b60bb4cb3fe7bd806e4eea7d4a533134","tid":1261174,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T06:09:20.000Z","msg":"月27日消息 根據京東方官方的消息，6月26日，在上海開幕的DISPLAY CHINA2019（國際新型顯示技術展）上，京東方展示了BD Cell顯示屏，官方稱BD Cell顯示屏是TFT-LCD技術的全新突破。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2019/6/20190627_105911_235.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ithome.com%2Fnewsuploadfiles%2F2019%2F6%2F20190627_105911_235.jpg&h=d0e41578&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據介紹，通過采用黑白和彩色的雙層Cell設計，以及像素分區技術以及微米級超精細控光技術，BD Cell顯示屏對比度達到百萬級，暗色調表現更加深邃。<br />\n<br />\n與OLED顯示相比，BD Cell顯示屏的低灰階畫面細節更加豐富，功耗可低於同尺寸OLED顯示屏40%，具有極強沖擊力的色彩表現及超高清HDR。<br />\n<br />\n最後，京東方表示海信搭載京東方BD Cell顯示屏的超高清電視產品即將上市。"},{"pid":"000b973cf48068ffcc3ddbdd977dae7b8feb0ad3","tid":1261174,"uid":41545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T23:00:28.000Z","msg":"係咪中國科技黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n純技術討論係好野黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"287a70ea4f79b0e69fdc1253a76201d85cf4dc96","tid":1261174,"uid":216417,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"000b973cf48068ffcc3ddbdd977dae7b8feb0ad3","tid":1261174,"uid":41545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T23:00:28.000Z","msg":"係咪中國科技黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n純技術討論係好野黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":